{{Otheruses|Spider}}
'''''Spider''''' was the designation of a pair of [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvettes]] belonging to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. They responded to a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] attack at a cargo transfer area where new surveillance probes were to be delivered by the [[BFF-1 bulk freighter/Legends|BFF-1 bulk freighter]] [[Libom]]. Both corvettes were disabled and destroyed by [[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander]] in a [[A/SF-01 B-wing starfighter/Legends|B-wing starfighter]].

